These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, country, disco, funk
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, azure, purple, turquise
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, ice-hockey, rugby, sailing
1. the person who likes turquise is the fan of disco##1
2. the fan of classical is on the far right##1
3. the person who likes lilac is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes purple is not the fan of classical##6
5. the person who's sport is rugby is not the person who likes turquise##6
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person who likes lilac##3
7. the person who likes lilac is somewhere between the fan of disco and the person who likes azure##7
8. the person who's sport is badminton is between the fan of country and the fan of disco##2
9. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | disco   | funk      | country   | classical  |
| Color   | turquise    | purple   | lilac | azure  |
| Sport         | sailing | badminton | rugby     | ice-hockey |

