.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, puzzles, photography, woodworking
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, indian, mexican, nigerian
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike, quad-bike, ship
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far right##1
2. the indian is the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the mexican is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
6. the argentine is the person driving the airplane##1
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
8. the person driving the ship is somewhere between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is photography##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby   | puzzles    | gardening     | woodworking   | photography      |
| Nationality   | indian    | argentine | mexican | nigerian  |
| Transport     | motorbike | airplane  | ship    | quad-bike |

