1. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
2. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the left of the indonesian##5
3. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to venice##5
4. the fan of d&b is between the indonesian and the person traveling to miami##2
5. the nigerian is not the fan of r&b##6
6. the person traveling to liverpool is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to venice##5
7. the person traveling to miami is the mexican##1
8. the indonesian is on the left or right of the person traveling to liverpool##3
9. the nigerian is somewhere between the person traveling to venice and the fan of blues##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3      |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | blues   | d&b        | r&b        | rock   |
| Nationality   | mexican | nigerian   | indonesian | french |
| City           | miami  | boston | venice       | liverpool |

