 1. the american is somewhere to the left of the person playing snooker##5
 2. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 3. the person playing domino is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person playing monopoly is between the canadian and the egyptian##2
 5. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the right of the turkish##5
 6. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
 7. the canadian is not the person drinking fanta##6
 8. the person playing billiard is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the person drinking soy-milk##7
 9. the american is somewhere to the left of the egyptian##5
10. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
11. the american is between the egyptian and the canadian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | sprite     | fanta      | milk     |
| Nationality   | turkish  | canadian   | american   | egyptian |
| Game     | domino     | billiard | monopoly | snooker   |

