5. the librarian is somewhere to the left of the coach##5
6. the chef is on the left of the librarian##1
7. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3
8. the person watching scientific movies is not the person who's sport is skiing##6
9. the person watching mystery movies is the person who's sport is badminton##1

